
'''= simple system for storing and transferring IOUs (credits) between agents'''

URL = http://www.webcredits.org/

=Description=

"Web Credits is an ultra simple system for storing and transferring IOUs (credits) between agents.

The aim of this spec is not to exceed 2 pages, be usable to create distributed payments, and arbitrarily extensible to add encryption, workflow, trust and aggregation systems of your chosing.

95%+ of the money in the world is in the form of an IOU. A bank balance is an IOU from the bank to you, Cash is often an IOU from a govt. to an individual.

The protocol is inspired by the Linked Data and PaySwarm standards, and is a usable subset that focuses on the data layer (JSON) and communication to apps (HTTP)."
(http://www.webcredits.org/)


